{"tid":230011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"應屆DSE女生   長洲企圖跳海獲救","createTime":"2017-05-05T04:45:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T05:11:50.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7635b26264510154c8a9acf07385cf0dbdbc8336","tid":230011,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T04:45:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170505/large/1493954890_67c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170505%2Flarge%2F1493954890_67c3.jpg&h=ab5462ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早上10時25分，一名少女在長洲國民路13號對開的海傍企圖跳海自殺。幸有街坊手急眼快將她拉住，並致電報警。救護員到場將少女送到醫院檢查，現場消息稱，少女17歲，是應屆DSE考生，疑不堪讀書壓力大而一時鑽牛角尖。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288"},{"pid":"384f1e997d5de30e62d66f02c7bd9dbb489f212f","tid":230011,"uid":26766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T04:50:50.000Z","msg":"又要比人屈入青山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5fb184c6b298a71925a233610a0c97c4ca48e93","tid":230011,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T05:10:19.000Z","msg":"係都等放榜先排IFC啦"},{"pid":"fc0616e85d480d62929b56a0c82a9286e89c6d3a","tid":230011,"uid":16775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T05:11:50.000Z","msg":"點解張圖左睇右睇都覺得係個中年/老年姐姐黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}